細胞培養與操作室、低溫操作冷房、控溫照光藻類培養室、各式分析儀器包括MALDI-TOF/MS；GC/MS；CE；FT/IR；HPLC/PDA,/UV, 
                              /FL, /RI, /EC, /ELSD；UV-Vis Spectrophotometer；Fluorescence 
                              Spectrophotometer；Microplate Reader；Electrophoresis；Fluorescent/, 
                              Phase Contrast/, DIC/, Inverted/ Microscope。





 

